<a href="/articles/25814.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/25814/indexMediumPc2/25814.jpg?1461210894" alt="腾讯投资的创业公司都从宝马挖了哪些人？">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/4/medium/4.png?1411569452" alt="智能">
			<span>智能</span>
		</p>
